<title>Justin Elie, Haitian Composer & Pianist</title>
<meta name="keywords" content="Haitian Composer, Haitian Pianist, Justin Elie">
<meta name="description" content="Justin Elie (1883-1931) was a Haitian classical composer and pianist who showed great talent at an early age.  He graduated from the Paris Conservatory in 1905.">
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 6.0">
