				</span>Première: Washington DC; Les Petits Chanteurs de Ste. 
				Trinité; Janus Smith, conductor.</font></span></p>
				<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
				<font face="Arial" size="2"><b style><i style>
				<font face="Verdana">6 Haitian meringues.</font></i></b><a style title name="_ftnref1" href="mhtml:mid://00000281/#_ftn1"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style><i style><font face="Verdana">[1]</font></i></span></span></a></font></p>
