				<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
				<font face="Arial" size="2"><b style><i style>
				<font face="Verdana">Bachanale.</font></i></b></font></p>
				<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
				<font face="Verdana" size="2"><b style><i style>Ballet 
				vaudouesque</i></b>, for orchestra (1921).<span style>&nbsp; </span>
				Première: 1922;<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; USA.</font></p>
				<p style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
				<font face="Verdana" size="2"><b style><i>Chants de la montagne</i></b>,<a style title name="_ftnref2" href="mhtml:mid://00000281/#_ftn2"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style>[2]</span></span></a> 
