				<p style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
				<span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Verdana" size="2">CD: 
				Jean Ernst Saint-Éloi, guitar, MIDI realised.<span style>&nbsp;
