				<p style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
				<font face="Verdana" size="2"><b style><i>----- 5. Nocturne; 
				Ancient mountain legend</i></b>, for piano.<span style>&nbsp; </span>
				New York: G. Schirmer.<span style>&nbsp; </span>Library: Spingarn.</font></p>
				<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
				<font face="Verdana" size="2"><b style><i style>Cléopatre</i></b>, 
				for orchestra.</font></p>
				<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
				<font face="Arial" size="2"><b style><i style>
